<C>__{kitchen maid}
<D>__{i found her sobbing her eyes out. poor thing, i said, what's all this? and she spilled her heart to me about master victor. how she'd always loved him, and now he was coming home to marry mistress elizabeth.}
<A>__{a murmur sweeps the courtroom. victor and elizabeth share a stunned glance.}
<C>__{kitchen maid}
<D>__{she cried and cried about the beautiful locket he'd sent. how she wished it was hers. she swore me never to tell a soul.}
